snippet.textDisplay: Gurdas man outshines diljit dosanjh . I am proud to meet Gurdas maan ji in my childhood many times when my mother was working as an officer in doordarshan and he used to come and sing there every week. He is very humble man . He used to fold his hand and say sat sri akaal to my mother . He is very good human being . Hats off gurdas maan ji . Still reviving child old memories.
